text: Graptocorixa is a genus of water boatmen in the family Corixidae. There are about six described species in Graptocorixa. ==Species== * Graptocorixa abdominalis (Say, 1832) * Graptocorixa californica (Hungerford, 1925) * Graptocorixa gerhardi (Hungerford, 1925) * Graptocorixa serrulata (Uhler, 1897) * Graptocorixa uhleri (Hungerford, 1925) * Graptocorixa uhleroidea Hungerford, 1938 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * Category:Graptocorixini Category:Nepomorpha genera
